{"tid":1231954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英華侯任校長  陳美娟：「普教中」不變","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T11:36:55.000Z","uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68554f960ce0bfc874be00d00269fba3bb4016d4","tid":1231954,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"陳美娟強調暫<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不打算改變現狀，「普教中」不會變。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n臨近暑假，又到各大直資學校陸續舉行明年入學簡介會的時候，備受家長歡迎的傳統直資男校，英華小學今起一連兩日舉辦5場小一入學簡介會，即將退休的校長林浣心，以及候任校長陳美娟一同現身台上，向家長介紹其教育理念以及英華小學收生安排。<br />\n<br />\n有家長擔心候任校長上場後學校教學有大轉變，例如她曾表示對普通話教中文成效有保留，特意問中文科是否保留「普教中」。陳美娟即表示，過往言談是以她所任職的那所學校為例，認為全用「普教中」對學習差異較大的學生而言並不適合，但以她所見，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">英華小學的學生可以很好掌握普通話，所以暫不打算改變現狀，「普教中」不會變。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4556195-英華小一簡介會-候任校長陳美娟：「普教中」不會?current_cat=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F4556195-%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%80%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8B%E6%9C%83-%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%99%B3%E7%BE%8E%E5%A8%9F%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%E6%99%AE%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%3Fcurrent_cat%3D3&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=6c77e29c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4556195-英華小一簡介會-候任校長陳美娟：「普教中」不會?current_cat=3</a>"},{"pid":"5db0fb9c3b59b26bd9ace003752520c80d171ff9","tid":1231954,"uid":226548,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lam_Y9yiD_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flam_Y9yiD_1200x0.png&h=ad0f6df1&s={SIZE}\" />"}